DESCRIPTION:Cecile Moroni is a French-Norwegian stand-up comedian with a sh
 arp eye and international energy. Cécile takes the audience through cultu
 re clashes\, Norwegian working life\, gender equality\, waffle Fridays\, a
 nd the eternal mystery: the Christmas party. Intelligent\, self-ironic\, a
 nd spot-on humour!
LOCATION:The Storm Stage
SUMMARY:Cecile Moroni
